description:
A third-year student in the piloting department. He serves as the deputy leader of http://anidb.net/ch125792 [Jeturk House]. As http://anidb.net/ch124442 [Guel]`s half-sibling by another mother, Lauda is actually his younger brother even though they are in the same school year. Unlike his brother, he is cool and rational.
Source: Official page
name: Lauda Neill
